profile:
With over a thousand stores worldwide, we not only have enormous buying power, but we have partners in all of the major brands, mills, and manufacturers. We’ve done the research for you. Just tell us your needs, and we’ll satisfy them beyond your expectations. We offer the largest selection of carpet, hardwood, laminate, ceramic tile, vinyl, area rugs and more - and you'll always find the best products and great savings... everyday. Each Carpet One Floor & Home flooring store is locally owned and operated. We are your neighbors. We work and live in your community and understand your needs. So you can expect integrity, the very best personal service, value, and warranties.

We can be reached at 604.463.7755 or email steve@mapleridgecarpetone.com

profile:
We are a family run business located in Port Coquitlam. We specialize in Hard-Surface Flooring Options for all residential applications and commercial. Our team of experts are always available to answer questions and provide you with quality customer service at an affordable price. Visit our website to view our Supplied & Installed with Underlay Specials on Laminate, European and German inspired beautiful wide planks. AC4 and FloorScore Certified, 5" and 7" wide planks available. 
In house installation team with project manager for all installations, WCB and Liability Insurance Available upon request.
